<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Outline on luoboQAQ</title><link>https://lbqaq.top/tags/outline/</link><description>Recent content in Outline on luoboQAQ</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 14:44:03 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://lbqaq.top/tags/outline/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用outline自建文档库</title><link>https://lbqaq.top/p/deploy-outline/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 14:44:03 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://lbqaq.top/p/deploy-outline/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://lbqaq.top/p/deploy-outline/125435446.webp" alt="Featured image of post 使用outline自建文档库" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;在去年的时候，就已经有了搭建一个私有的文档库的想法了。当时是采用gitlab作为OIDC认证源，但是gitlab实在是太吃资源了，内存不一会就被吃满了。后面又去调研了一些开源自建的OIDC认证源项目，无一例外这些项目都很复杂，从而这个想法就被搁置了。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>